<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <link href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">    
  <meta name="apple-touch-fullscreen" content="yes">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes"> 
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
  <title>Mission Control - Investigating <%= company.name %></title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon"/>
  <link rel="icon" href="favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon"/>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="small">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h1>Investigating <%= company.name %></h1>
      <nav>
        <a href="/companies" class="btn">All Companies</a>
        <a href="/companies/new" class="btn">New Company</a>
        <a href="/investigations" class="btn">Investigations</a>
        <a href="/news_sources" class="btn">All News Sources</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h3>Submitting a Mission Statement Proof</h3>
      <p>When providing evidence of the above mission statement, please try to explain your findings in a simple impartial way, this proof will be available to general public and will be associated with both you and your organisation. For your reference the company mission statement is below.</p>
      <form action="/investigations" method="POST">
        <input type="hidden" name="company_id" value="<%= company.id %>"/>
        <textarea name="mission_statement_proof" placeholder="mission statement proof"></textarea>
        <input type="text" name="mission_statement_investigator" placeholder="investigator name" />
        <input type="submit" value="submit" class="btn" />
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <h3><%= company.name %></h3>
      <p><%= company.mission_statement.gsub(/[\r\n]+/, "<br>") %></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>